Sino-Telecom specializes in high-end networking equipment for communications, network visibility, and AI infrastructure. We serve carriers and enterprises clients in over 30 countries worldwide.
Networking: DCI, OTN, 5G Fronthaul, PON OLT, IP RAN, Switch;
Network Visibility: Traffic Analysis, DPI, Big Data Platform;
AI Infrastructure: AI Switch, Optical Interconnect, Integrated Solutions.

The Ministry of High-Tech Industry is a central body of executive authority developing and implementing the RA Government’s policy in the high-tech sphere. 
The Ministry develops and implements the policy of the Government of the Republic of Armenia in the following areas:
•	High technology,
•	Information technology,
•	Information Security,
•	Digitalization,
•	Post,
•	Communication,
•	International cooperation,
•	Licensing,
•	Space,
•	Military industry.
Under the leadership of the Ministry of High-Tech Industry of the Republic of Armenia:
